works.description: The contemporary designs from Paris-based T.T.Trunks are second to none when it comes to aesthetics, functionality and luxury. The French house has earlier impressed us with their contemporary trunks, including the pool & spa trunk and the new Dandy Trunk with a built-in iPad holder. On the occasion of the Madison Avenue Watch Week that was held in New York (April 11-16), T.T.Trunks revealed two of its new designs - the Travel Watch and the Week End Watch trunks - dedicated to watch collectors and to those who are fascinated by the luxury watchmaking world.
